{"tid":2232592,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"༄༊࿆獵魔士༊࿆࿐第二季Geralt盔甲升級造型曝光！","createTime":"2020-10-06T13:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T14:50:34.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef323a56debb7dcbf632ed0e8edac6d6cc021c9","tid":2232592,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFAxBqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFAxBqb.jpg&h=97619561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ieXTkRR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FieXTkRR.jpg&h=f4594d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[HK01]Netflix今日（6/10）在Twitter公開了最新劇照，見到主角Geralt of Rivia（Henry Cavill飾）的盔甲全面升級的造型終於曝光！<br />\n<br />\n另外，製作人Lauren S. Hissrich早前接受外國傳媒訪問時，率先透露了第二季將會有超過8個心角色加入。除了有《嗜血嬌娃》（Killing Eve）的Kim Bodnia飾演經驗老到的獵魔士Vesemir之外，HBO神劇《權力遊戲》（Game of Thrones）中飾演Tormund的Kristofer Hivju將會飾演一名受了詛咒，外貌如野獸的男子。至於劇情方面，第二季不會再以三條時間線來敘事，並會探索主角Geralt成為獵魔士的背景。不過第二季原定在2021年上架，目前還未知道會否因疫情而延遲計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWZa7yv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWZa7yv.jpg&h=9d07d015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKim Bodnia <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zf7Dw0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZf7Dw0n.jpg&h=f771f901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKristofer Hivju"},{"pid":"8d3609257866c5d1bff18a4cbc1a57a365efb656","tid":2232592,"uid":63412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"三條線其實幾正 可以估估下"}]}